{"tid":1502043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25/8 荃葵青 點解冇人提？","createTime":"2019-08-24T14:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:47:52.000Z","uid":248384,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca430f52e7bf0f4a9545d5fb428ace683ca0b7a","tid":1502043,"uid":248384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e27712d4fe0fbd5408c27a96eafc151b90754c","tid":1502043,"uid":248384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"Why?"},{"pid":"f59029b2f7059eb2d4253346ed0664db48ad6ee1","tid":1502043,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:31:56.000Z","msg":"完埋今晚先"},{"pid":"50c7849d495200be6912f4105c5707fe9e08151d","tid":1502043,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:32:58.000Z","msg":"你去埋我果份"},{"pid":"0d29ff6640bb5950098585e3df7df4efc957275c","tid":1502043,"uid":282490,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:33:29.000Z","msg":"堅持揸緊春袋/有車嘅手足，請聽朝九點出發 有好多人去<br />\n就會引更多人去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如堅持遊行嘅手足 請<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n兩邊都去plz </span></strong></span><br />\n遊完就入機場幫拖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地要長時間塞<br />\n就要keep 住一車車巴士地鐵無間斷流入機場<br />\n<br />\n朝早塞完比人趕返出黎嘅 下午剛好可以遊行<br />\n遊行行到終點就一齊去機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本聽日荃葵青就係天意！<br />\n仲有邊區入機場有咁撚方便？！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nRecap:<br />\n<br />\n方案一：<br />\n朝早入機場嘅人下午去遊行<br />\n方案二：<br />\n下午遊行嘅人遊完去機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n流水式集會2.0 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入機場原因：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我而家搵到個制衡狗隊濫暴方法<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n[班勇武手足可能一直都去錯地方] 聽朝還眼楂緊政府春袋集會!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong>"},{"pid":"73eb6723f9171656013e1db76f993a154c22b385","tid":1502043,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"我見好似冇人講825荃葵青大遊行？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501064</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b80a282eb6de2dc71edc1400635eddf1735f811","tid":1502043,"uid":248384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73eb6723f9171656013e1db76f993a154c22b385","tid":1502043,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"我見好似冇人講825荃葵青大遊行？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501064</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"都係好小人提 因為有同其他活動衝突？<br />\n唔明點解"},{"pid":"dcad07029650f001a49cb4087fcf45c6bf1a9e15","tid":1502043,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b80a282eb6de2dc71edc1400635eddf1735f811","tid":1502043,"uid":248384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73eb6723f9171656013e1db76f993a154c22b385","tid":1502043,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"我見好似冇人講825荃葵青大遊行？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501064</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"都係好小人提 因為有同其他活動衝突？<br />\n唔明點解"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"因為好多人無啦啦話改去機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34df215fde31974b66b5cf59db322c39227e9dd6","tid":1502043,"uid":169687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YdTDf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A